The paper discusses the problem of developing RL methods that obtain optimal decisions in a non-stationary environment. This problem is related to several sub-fields of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), control systems (cs.SY), robotics (cs.RO), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.RO, and cs.NE, in that order.
